ications</span>.\n\nBuccaneer coating solutions have a 35-year history of development and application in the United Kingdom and South Africa. Over the years applications have spread throughout South Africa, the Benelux Countries, Iceland and Canada.\n\nAt Buccaneer, our mission is to produce the highest quality coatings utilizing our proprietary formulations with uncompromising raw material inputs. Combing ease of use and superior durability provides a cost effective and long term coating solution for our customers while respecting the environment by using only eco-friendly acceptable raw materials that are not hazardous to people, animals or the environment.','About','','inherit','open','open','','38-revision','','','2013-01-05 21:47:00','2013-01-06 04:47:00','',38,'http://buccaneerprotectivecoatings.com/2013/01/05/38-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(40,1,'2013-01-05 21:48:13','2013-01-06 04:48:13','','Overview','','publish','open','open','','40','','','2013-02-13 21:56:22','2013-02-14 04:56:22','',0,'http://buccaneerprotectivecoatings.com/?p=40',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(41,1,'2013-01-05 21:48:52','2013-01-06 04:48:52','One of the first questions we typically get at Buccaneer is “why plastic, why not paint?”. Liquid plastic applications have proved themselves as far more durable than conventional paints and varnishes.\r\n\r\nPlastics do not degrade over time or become a hazard. Instead, they protect and preserve the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">surfaces</span> <i>(link to applications)</i> to which they are applied.\r\n\r\nExtensive research and development has lead to the advancement of proprietary resins and entirely unique formulations. Buccaneer Liquid Applied Protection can be applied to all types of <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">surfaces</span> <i>(link to applications)</i> including steel, wood, concrete and plaster. The unique <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">chemical formula</span> <i>(link to liquid applied protection)</i> of this product line allows for maximum durability that will outperform virtually all conventional paint products and give any building or structure a far superior life span dramatically reducing expensive maintenance costs.\r\n\r\nBuccaneer offers both water based and solvent based protective coating solutions based on the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">application</span> required.','Liquid Applied Protection','','publish','open','open','','liquidappliedprotection','','','2013-01-06 21:25:12','2013-01-07 04:25:12','',0,'http://buccaneerprotectivecoatings.com/?page_id=41',0,'page','',0),(42,1,'2013-01-05 21:48:23','2013-01-06 04:48:23','','Liquid Plastic Coating','','inherit','open','open','','41-revision','','','2013-01-05 21:48:23','2013-01-06 04:48:23','',41,'http://buccaneerprotectivecoatings.com/2013/01/05/41-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(44,1,'2013-01-05 21:53:12','2013-01-06 04:53:12','Please read these terms of use carefully. By using this website, you agree to these Terms of Use without modification. Buccaneer Protective Coatings Ltd. (Buccaneer). has created this website for your use and information, subject to the following terms and conditions.\r\n\r\nGENERAL TERMS OF USE\r\nLimitations on Copying. Buccaneer grants to you a non-exclusive and non-transferable license to view and print documents and web pages located on this website for non-commercial use only. The information and content on this website is provided to you solely for the purpose of helping you understand the services available to you at Buccaneer. The documents and web pages on this website may not be reproduced, republished, retransmitted, sold, modified or exploited in any way. Any printed copies of these web pages must retain, without modification any proprietary notices.\r\n\r\nLinked Internet Sites. Buccaneer may provide links to other Internet sites as a convenience to you. The content on these linked sites does not necessarily reflect the opinion of Buccaneer and