cation</span> required.','Liquid Applied Protection','','inherit','open','open','','41-revision-2','','','2013-01-05 21:48:52','2013-01-06 04:48:52','',41,'http://buccaneerprotectivecoatings.com/2013/01/05/41-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(62,1,'2013-01-19 16:46:52','2013-01-19 23:46:52','','Testimonial Fields','','publish','closed','closed','','acf_testimonial-fields','','','2013-01-19 16:47:40','2013-01-19 23:47:40','',0,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/?post_type=acf&#038;p=62',0,'acf','',0),(64,1,'2013-01-19 16:48:46','2013-01-19 23:48:46','Buccaneer Storm Seal HD is long-lasting. We have applications that were applied 30 years ago and still withstand the elements.','Basil Smit, Manager Engineering Services, Kromco','','publish','closed','closed','','64','','','2013-01-19 16:49:00','2013-01-19 23:49:00','',0,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=64',0,'testimonial','',0),(65,1,'2013-01-19 16:49:16','2013-01-19 23:49:16','Since our introduction to Buccaneer, we have chosen to use their products  due to quality, durability, good service & sound technical advice.','WM Geldenhuys, Dcore Properties','','publish','closed','closed','','wm-geldenhuys-dcore-properties','','','2013-01-19 16:49:16','2013-01-19 23:49:16','',0,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=65',0,'testimonial','',0),(66,1,'2013-01-19 16:49:34','2013-01-19 23:49:34','The professional support service from Buccaneer is one of the best.','Basil Smit, Manager Engineering Services, Kromco','','publish','closed','closed','','basil-smit-manager-engineering-services-kromco','','','2013-01-19 16:49:34','2013-01-19 23:49:34','',0,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=66',0,'testimonial','',0),(67,1,'2013-01-19 16:49:51','2013-01-19 23:49:51','We recommend Buccaneer as a supplier for roofing products.','Andrew van Zyl, Director, Storm Roofing','','publish','closed','closed','','andrew-van-zyl-director-storm-roofing','','','2013-01-19 16:49:51','2013